## Cutover sequence

1. Box base + Tailscale + mosh, confirm `rc` from the Mac lands in a tmux shell.  ✅ checkpoint: `rc` works.
2. Clone `~/.claude`, `bun install` (Pulse + Observability), restore `.env`, `claude` auth.  ✅ checkpoint: `claude` runs over `rc`.
3. Fix the `Pulse`/`PULSE` casing, patch `manage.sh`/`start-pulse.sh` for Linux.  ✅ checkpoint: `bun run pulse.ts` starts clean.
4. Install systemd units, `enable-linger`, enable timers.  ✅ checkpoint: `systemctl --user list-timers` shows daily/weekly; Pulse survives a reboot.
5. Browser to `http://box:31337` over Tailscale.  ✅ checkpoint: Pulse + TELOS page render.
6. Demote Telegram to push-only; first cadence digest arrives at 06:30.  ✅ checkpoint: digest in Telegram, generated on the box.
7. Stand up git remote + restic timer + Mac cold-standby clone.  ✅ checkpoint: a test `restic restore` works.

Each checkpoint is a stop-and-verify gate. Do not advance on assumption.

